      "width": 300.40000000000003,
      "height": 160.0,
      "text": "Supertype over everything Verity governs.\n\n{ Agent | Task | Prompt | Tool | Pipeline\u2020 }\n\nTables:\n\u2022 agent, task, prompt, tool\n\u2022 pipeline \u2020(deprecated 2026-04-24)\n\u2022 *_version (7-state lifecycle)\n\u2022 entity_prompt_assignment\n  (polymorphic to {Agent,Task} versions)",
