      "text": "Sub-supertype: things that actually run.\n\n{ Agent | Task }\nParity on input_schema / output_schema /\nwiring / tools / inference_config.\n\nJunctions:\n\u2022 agent_version_tool\n\u2022 task_version_tool\n\u2022 agent_version_delegation\n  (parent\u2192child, name or version)\n\u2022 inference_config (shared)",
