      "text": "Unified reference grammar:\n  input.* / output.* / const:* / fetch:C/M(...)\n\nTables (new):\n\u2022 source_binding (owner_kind poly)\n\u2022 write_target (owner_kind poly)\n\u2022 target_payload_field (weak)\n\nLegacy (migration window):\n\u2022 task_version_source\u2020\n\u2022 task_version_target\u2020",
