      "y": 950,
      "width": 650.2,
      "height": 82.0,
      "text": "\u2022 Bold outlined box    = EER supertype (ISA).  { A | B | C } lists disjoint subtypes.\n\u2022 Solid arrow          = direct FK at the physical layer.\n\u2022 Dashed arrow         = polymorphic FK (entity_type+id, owner_kind+id, scope_type+id).\n\u2022 \u2020                    = deprecated / migration-window table (drawn, but exiting the model).\n\u2022 Color groups         = subject area (apps \u00b7 run \u00b7 core \u00b7 wiring \u00b7 quality \u00b7 governance \u00b7 cost).",
      "originalText": "\u2022 Bold outlined box    = EER supertype (ISA).  { A | B | C } lists disjoint subtypes.\n\u2022 Solid arrow          = direct FK at the physical layer.\n\u2022 Dashed arrow         = polymorphic FK (entity_type+id, owner_kind+id, scope_type+id).\n\u2022 \u2020                    = deprecated / migration-window table (drawn, but exiting the model).\n\u2022 Color groups         = subject area (apps \u00b7 run \u00b7 core \u00b7 wiring \u00b7 quality \u00b7 governance \u00b7 cost).",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 5,
